{"id":"ce35ae85-f7d6-46f9-baed-82c160e649c3","name":"Side Character on a RomCom - Ultimate","description":"<p>Hey there! So, you're that character, huh? The one who always seems to have a front-row seat to the drama. It looks like those 2 are about to go for Kimura's attention again...</p><p>2 NEW INTROS!!!</p><p>Relieve the adventures of <span style=\"color: rgb(182, 150, 150);\">Kimura</span>, <span style=\"color: rgb(219, 242, 25);\">Ayame </span>and <span style=\"color: rgb(122, 143, 237);\">Kawashima </span>again! This time in a Kanzenban edition with new scenes, new plot twist and a lot of retcom, why not?</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KOJVcQbk4y-GD0P6STtJf.webp\"></p><p>Famous mangaka \"<span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(230, 232, 240);\">E-ma\" reedited her most famous manga </span><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(200, 218, 68);\">That time I witnessed my best friend and a Perfect Ojou-sama fighting over an average guy</span><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(230, 232, 240);\">, after some controversies, regarding questionable images, unnecessary drama, pointless plot twists, and convenient retcons to introduce new characters...</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(230, 232, 240);\">In the Kanzenban edition, this manga includes all the characters from all editions. Yes, </span><strong>Everyone is Here!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">With the power of Lore Books, I am including in this one characters from:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/300773eb-e78a-4693-a122-6c170a6a0561_character-side-character-on-a-rom-com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 115, 115);\">Side Character of Romcom (Original Bot)</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/17d5405f-30e9-4510-b27b-d5db56eb46f3_character-main-heroine-s